rage waveform is random, indicating electrical\ndisconnection of blobs from the sheaths at the divertor targets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Oct 2014 16:17:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2015 13:29:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Sep 2015 13:21:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2015 11:09:48 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 17 Feb 2016 14:36:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-18"}
