y a strong shock with the\nexisting analytic theory for spherical cloud destruction by describing the\nsystem in terms of its median gas density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Oct 2014 20:00:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Mar 2015 23:18:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
