igger mechanism for coronal subflares is\nin other active regions, and how important it is for coronal heating in\ngeneral, remain to be seen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Oct 2014 00:04:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
