rain new stellar upper-atmosphere models\nfor cool stars and provide realistic inputs to models describing exoplanetary\nphotochemistry and atmospheric evolution in the absence of ultraviolet\nspectroscopy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Oct 2014 00:27:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
